language ESSENCE' 1.0
given     n : int
letting   RANGE be domain int(1..n)
letting   SYMBOLS be domain int(1..n)

find      field: matrix indexed by [RANGE, RANGE] of RANGE

such that
  $ all rows have to be different
  forAll row : RANGE .
       allDiff(field[row,..]),

  $ all columns have to be different
  forAll col : RANGE .
       allDiff(field[..,col])

